  "description": "A pluck that transforms. Fast attack (5ms), medium decay — by the time the transient decays the CA pattern has already shifted, creating a bell-into-texture morphing character. Rule 90 at medium evolution. Locked pitch mode keeps it melodic. Envelope amount routes to evolution rate so the attack kick-starts evolution. The note begins as a tone and ends as a pattern. Plays like a metallophone from another planet.",
